    Elément exp in (1) du thème
    <br />
    <div>
      <span>  {{ form_row(formphysaddtopic.contentexpin, {'attr': {'class': 'form-control'}}) }}  </span>
    </div>

    <br />
    Elément th (2) du thème
    <br />
    <div>
      <span>  {{ form_row(formphysaddtopic.contentth, {'attr': {'class': 'form-control'}}) }}  </span>
    </div>

    <br />
